FBIS3-39384 "drweu032_l_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-032 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Feb 1994 SPAIN Cuba to Pay Reparations to Spanish Nationals LD1502183294 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1700 GMT 15 Feb 94 LD1502183294 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Thirty-five years later, some 1,500 Spanish citizens will receive reparations for the expropriations that took place during the Cuban revolution. The sum of 5.3 billion pesetas was approved for reparations today. The money will be paid out by the Spanish state, which will in turn be paid back by Fidel Castro's regime.
